Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

###

### 2.16 GET Expedition Participants - Visitor (Expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expedition-participants
Authorization: Bearer {{visitorToken}}

###

### 2.17 DELETE Expedition Participant - Travel Manager (Expect 403 Audit Hard-Lock)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/expedition-participants/1
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}

