### ############################################################
### AUTOMATION TESTS - PROACTIVE LOGIC
### ############################################################

@autoExpeditionId = 1
@autoPersonId = 2

### [EXP-AUTO-01] Assign Participant to PLANNED Expedition
### Expected: create a notification of type EXPEDITION_RETURN.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expedition-participants
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expeditionId": {{autoExpeditionId}},
  "personId": {{autoPersonId}},
  "expeditionRole": "SCOUT",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### [EXP-AUTO-02] Verify notification in the assigned worker inbox
### Expected title: "Asignacion de expedicion".
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?type=EXPEDITION_RETURN&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###